OL,3,CMillions face higher council tax bills
OL,4,Cas government approves increases
OL,6,FMillions are facing higher-than-normal
OL,7,Fcouncil tax hikes as the government
OL,8,Fapproved requests for six local
OL,9,Fauthorities to increase their rates by
OL,10,Fmore than the usual amount.
OL,12,FDeputy Prime Minister Angela Rayner,
OL,13,Fwho approved the decision, said
OL,14,Fchallenges remain in the government's
OL,15,Fbid "to fix the broken system we
OL,16,Finherited", and stressed the need to
OL,17,Fstrike a balance between preventing
OL,18,Fcouncils from experiencing "further
OL,19,Ffinancial distress" and the "interests
OL,20,Fof taxpayers".
