OL,3,CMillions face higher council tax bills
OL,4,Cas government approves increases
OL,6,FSix councils, serving more than two
OL,7,Fmillion people in total, have been
OL,8,Fgranted permission to increase council
OL,9,Ftax beyond the established annual
OL,10,Fthreshold of 5%.
OL,12,FUsually, if councils want to increase
OL,13,Ftheir tax by more than 5% they must
OL,14,Fhave it approved by local referendum,
OL,15,Fbut Rayner's decision on Monday
OL,16,Fbypasses that step.
