OL,3,CMillions face higher council tax bills
OL,4,Cas government approves increases
OL,6,FBradford Council will be able to
OL,7,Fincrease the levy by 10%, while
OL,8,FWindsor and Maidenhead Council and
OL,9,FNewham Council can all increase bills
OL,10,Fby an additional 9%.
OL,12,FThe remaining councils ` Birmingham,
OL,13,FSomerset and Trafford ` have been
OL,14,Fgranted a further 7.5% uplift beyond
OL,15,Fthe threshold.
