OL,3,CMillions face higher council tax bills
OL,4,Cas government approves increases
OL,6,FExplaining the move in a written
OL,7,Fstatement, Ms Rayner said: "These are
OL,8,Fdifficult decisions that government
OL,9,Fhas not taken lightly. We recognise
OL,10,Fthe importance of limited increases in
OL,11,Fhelping to prevent these councils
OL,12,Ffalling further into financial
OL,13,Fdistress ` but we have been clear this
OL,14,Fmust be balanced with the interests of
OL,15,Ftaxpayers.
