OL,4,Cas government approves increases
OL,6,F"We have agreed to a limited number of
OL,7,Frequests and in all cases have not
OL,8,Fagreed to the full amount requested.
OL,9,FWhere we have agreed, it is only for
OL,10,Fcouncils with amongst the lowest
OL,11,Flevels of council tax, and where we
OL,12,Fexpect, even after these increases,
OL,13,Fresidents will still be paying less
OL,14,Fthan the average compared with similar
OL,15,Fcouncils."
