OL,4,Cas government approves increases
OL,6,FRayner's statement came alongside
OL,7,Fwider funding approved for councils
OL,8,Ffor this year, with no local authority
OL,9,Fseeing a reduction in core spending
OL,10,Fpower.
OL,12,FThe statement confirmed that councils
OL,13,Fwill have access to more than #69
OL,14,Fbillion in funding this year - a 6.8%
OL,15,Fincrease in cash terms compared to
OL,16,F2024-25.
