OL,6,FMs Rayner confirmed that #60 million
OL,7,Fhas been put aside for "long-term
OL,8,Fimprovements", including facilitating
OL,9,Ffurther a "devolution revolution" and
OL,10,Ffixing the system of local government
OL,11,Faudit which has been plagued by delays
OL,12,Fin recent years.
OL,14,FIn addition, the government is
OL,15,Fproviding up to #3.7 billion
OL,16,Fadditional funding to councils with
OL,17,Fsocial care responsibilities,
OL,18,Fincluding a #880 million boost to the
OL,19,FSocial Care Grant.
